  "description": "<p>The Big Agnes Divide Insulated Sleeping Pad offers the kind of warmth and cushioning backpackers dream about. Lightweight Thermolite\u00ae insulation combined with TPU lamination reflect heat back to you while you sleep. The durable recycled nylon ripstop fabric stands up to the rigours of life on the trail. Oversized outer tubes cradle you in the centre of the pad, preventing you from rolling off in the night.</p><ul><li>Made from lightweight recycled nylon ripstop for backcountry reliability</li><li>Super-durable aviation-grade TPU lamination prevents leaks and punctures</li><li>Large outer chambers keep you centred on the pad</li><li>Thermolite\u00ae Insulation with a heat reflective film that traps body heat and reflects it back at you to prevent heat loss</li><li>Minimalist I-Beam construction reduces weight and provides consistent stability and comfort</li><li>Antimicrobial treatment inside the pad prevents microorganism growth</li><li>High-volume dual valve allows for efficient and easy inflation, super-fast deflation, and micro adjustments</li><li>Includes pad inflation sack, protective storage sack, replacement valve seal, and repair patches</li></ul>",
